l preserve that nitrogen utilizing it for the plants. And so the first thing you want to do is hurry up and use that because nitrogen goes quick. Anyway that's one of the big things about gardening is you realize how quickly nitrogen depletion happens. And so a good way to just kind of prevent that is have large amounts of humus that's rich in nitrogen. You get that through a good hot compost because you're capturing that nitrogen. Cold compost just kind of sifts out also they stink. Anyway just want to make a video about nitrogen capture because it's so gosh dang important. Thanks y'all\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, why hot composting?\",\n      \"start\": 0.32,\n      \"end\": 3.04,\n      \"duration\": 2.72,\n      \"confidence\": 0.989,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.32,\n          \"end\": 0.56,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.982\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.72,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.8,\n          \"end\": 0.96,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 0.96,\n          \"end\": 1.2,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 1.2,\n          \"end\": 1.36,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \",\",\n          \"start\": 1.36,\n          \"end\": 1.6,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.923\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" wh\",\n          \"start\": 1.6,\n          \"end\": 1.76,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {